Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:01:00.68,Lyrics EN,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:08.76,Lyrics EN,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
