Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{破られた退部届}—Episode 009—\NTorn resignation letters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん。}Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよあたしたちの出番が来たようね。}At last it's time for our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{出番？}Your turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言う意味？}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはこの前のを返しをさせてもらうことよ。}We want to repay you for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{何ですって？}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{強がりを止しなさいよ。}Drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくらやっても、同じこと。}The results won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{二人共さ、休みの間にあたしたちXXなったって言うの？え？}Or maybe you've spent your spring break on some special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{まさか。ヘヘヘ。}As if, hahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{その通りよ。}That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、エープリルフールは過ぎたのよ。}Hey, April Fools is long over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{言っとくけどさ、この前実力で勝ったんですからね。}Just to make it clear: we've already proved our skill before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{お分かり？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{だから実力XXX返しようと言うの。}That's why we want to repay you with skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かる？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちにね…何時までも大きな顔させないてこと。分かる？}We won't let you keep that boastful attitude forever. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{よく分かったわ。}We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうやら、もう一度可愛がるほか成せそうだわね。}Looks like the last time wasn't enough for you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{馬鹿馬鹿しいじゃん。四天王XXXこんな(XXX・練習試合)にするなんて。}That's ridiculous. Our Big Four is too good to accept such a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからさ。ぐうの音もでないようにしてやるんだ。}No trash talk. We'll play with them all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{ファイト同じメンバーでいいのね。}We'll play with the same people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、いらっしゃい。}You've got your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわね。}Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{—やろう。\N—なによ。}– Let's do this.\N– What's with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{畜生。}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{やるの？}Are we really doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。本郷先生だわ。}Ah, it's professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生！}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{—先生！\N—先生！}– Professor!\N– Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生、富士見の生徒XXXために来たんですか？}Professor, did you come to be Fujimi students' good charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{何？}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの梶岡先生下ろして、コーチに売り込んだ。そういうつもりなんでしょうね。}You've taken place of our professor Kajioka as the new coach to promote yourself, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{なに言ってるの。}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな本郷先生じゃないのよ。}Professor Hongou is not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、なぜ無理にコーチに成ろうとしたのよ。}Then why did he push to become our coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん…}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン！黙って！}Hmph. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん、どうしたんだろう。}I wonder what's with Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{何かが変よ。}She's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{許せないわ。}I won't forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部員としてあたしたちを除け者にしようなんて…}As the club members, for you to cast us out…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言うことなのよ？}What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生。}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{何とか言ったらどうなんです？}How about you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。本郷先生。}That's right. Professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな人怒鳴りつけて…}She's yelling so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX・思い出したと驚かないわよ。}You two stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと、先生！}What it'll be, professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{何だ、その言い方は。}What's with your way of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{生徒は先生に大して聞く口じゃないな。}Students these days have no respect at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、ま良い。}Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなことと言っても、君達は勝手に今日XXだろう。}Even if you say this, you come here as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{俺に言えるはただ一つ。}I will say just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部はバレーの実力は第一だ。}In the volleyball, the skill is the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{所で、その実力でお返しすると言っただようだが？}By the way, I believe you said you want a grudge match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{言いました。}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{—親分…\N—だって、あたしじゃん…}– Chief…\N– We're no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{面白いわ。}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、あんたたち…}Well then, you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生の前でゆっくりとその実力を見せてもらいましょうね。}Ket's see your skills before your beloved professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうする？}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{まあまあことないよ。}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生が言ったんだもん。勝ってんかってにやっつけちゃうよ。}The teacher nailed it. We'll just kick their butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く。}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。やろうやろう。}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{実力でお返しすると言った、君達の言葉を信じよう。}"Repay with skill." I'll believe those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{頼むぞ、鮎原。}I'm counting on you, Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん、一歩一歩一本。}Ayuhara-san, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{—頑張ってね！\N—キャプテン。}– Do your best!\N– Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{—あ！\N—お！}– Ah!\N– Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{変化球。}The curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{「木の葉落とし」。}"Leaf Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{フフン。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへへ。}Fufufu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{何よぼやぼやしてるの？}Why are you spacing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ポイントよ、得点。}It's a point for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{得点をXXX。}We scored one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{はーはい、ただいま。}Y-Yes ma'am! Right away.
