Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{アン。}Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁ…}Ahh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{痛い。}It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{痛い…}It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{又手が痺れた…}My hand got numb again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしよう？}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さん！}Ah, Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{わい、キャプテン！いいぞ、いいぞ！}Waii, captain! Nice, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん、すこしXXXやったら？}Ayuhara-san, maybe we should go easy on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{わい、(XXX・いいね、ふたり、いいね)。}Waii, good going, good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{わあい！}Waai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほ？}Ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原所か、早川であの変化球サーブを…}Besides Ayuhara, Hayakawa can serve that curve ball too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんだけの変化球と思った、間違いよ。}If you thought I'd lose to Ayuhara-san, big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{いかが？}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さん、すごい！}Hayakawa-san, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{信じられないわ。}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなに調子良く決まるなんて不思議なくらいだわ。}It feels so strange when we're leading this easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{合宿XXこんなに覿面だなんて…}I didn't think the camp would be this effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたち以上面食らってるのはあそこにいるわ。}But looks like our surprise can't compare with theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けたくない。}I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けられないわ。}I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{絶対に。}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}No way we'll lose!…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}No way we'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるもんか！}No way we'll lose!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉は無理になって、調子を崩している。}Izumi became unreasonable and lost her rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{—はい。\N—それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あぁぁ！}Aaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい、セットいただきよ！}All right! We won this set!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{わい、YYY皆YYY！}Waai, you did well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、痛い。}Ah, it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分、すごい。}Chief, that was terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{左手あんなに打てるなんてさ！}The way you served with your left hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{それも強烈！コートは(XXX・凹みそうな)スパイクね。}And that strength. That spike could dent the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう？今の鮎原さんの実力よ？}How did you like current Ayuhara-san's skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん…}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けたわ。}We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうーどうして？未だ勝負がこれからよ。}Wh-What are you saying? The match starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{ワンセット終わったばかりじゃない…}It's ridiculous to decide it with a single set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{弱き出さないで、泉さん。}Stay strong, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{—あ、泉さん…\N—泉さん。}– Ah, Izumi-san.\N– Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くん！}Izumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたんだ、泉？}What's wrong, Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう駄目よ。}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{この手が言うこと聞かないわ。}This hand just won't react.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{—泉さん！\N—泉さん！}– Izumi-san!\N– Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{—泉さん。\N—泉さんたら…}– Izumi-san.\N– Izumi-san, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜ途中でXXX？泉さんらしくないわね。}Why did we give up midway? That's not like you, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{何セットやっても、同じことよ。}Any more sets wouldn't change the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{—え？\N—え？}– Eh?\N– Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな…}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなバカな…}That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしには分かってるんだ。}Don't argue with me. I know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{悔しいけど、先に帰るわ。}It's regrettable. I'll be going home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん…}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうかしてるんじゃない？}That was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さんらしくないわ。}Ah, it's so unlike Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{なるほど。}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{大学の合宿に参加したのか。}So it was university training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{道理で。}That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかし、辛かったろう。}But it must've been tough, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、四天王に勝ったですもの。}But we won with the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{すかっとしました。}I feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分てんでススーパーマンだったわよ。}Chief, you were like Superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さんだって、あんな変化球出すなんて…}Hayakawa-san's curve ball was awesome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当、格好良かったわ。}Yeah. It was super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{これでやっとあたしたちのバレー部らしく成った}It finally feels like volleyball club again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。二度とあんなやつに口じゃさせないわ。}Yeah. I don't want to hear their boasting ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{天狗の鼻を折られて、ぺっちゃんこ。}They couldn't see past the end of their noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ざまあご覧、遊ばせって。}In the end they had to bump into a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{ヘヘヘ。}Heheheh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ…}Aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{お終いだわ、四天王もう。}The Big Four is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、鮎原。}However, Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{これから一体どうするつもりだ？}What do you want to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王…このまま仲間外れにしておくのうかない？}Don't you want to fix your relationship with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原達ともかく、他のメンバーと比べたら彼女達の方がはるかに実力は上だ。}With the exception of Ayuhara's group, when compared to other members, they are stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは君達を認めるな。}I'm sure you understand that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、先生。}But professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんな非協力的な人たちとチーム組むなんてあたしたちはできないわ。}It's futile for us to try joining forces with such uncooperative people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{ヘヘヘ。}Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{できるかできんかは、それはま、君達に任せよう。}Futile or not, I'm entrusting it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いな？鮎原。早川。}God it? Ayuhara. Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？香取さん、どうするのよ。}Katori-san, what will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちがその気なら、しょうがないな。}If you feel this way, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、決まった。}It's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんに話して、明日は四人一緒に退部届けよう。}After telling Izumi-san, let's put our resignation together tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{了解。}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{誰があんなバレー部いてやるもんですか。}Who'd want to be in that club anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・黄線)だ!}Keep it straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{ファイト、ファイト！}Fight, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{ぼやぼやするな！}Don't space out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{良く玉を見ろ！}Watch the ball closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生あんなこと言うけど、}No matter what professor said…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理よね。}It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理って？}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王きっと止めちゃうわ、バレー部を。}The Big Four are sure to quit the club now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{やめさせるわけにはいかないわ。}We can't let them do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち先じゃ大変な戦力低下よ。}Our power will fall considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{弱気な、鮎原さん。}That's weak, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王なんかいなくだって、あたしたちって十分やっていけるわ。}Even without the Big Four we're plenty capable on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、それはどうかしら。}Ah, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{今の泉さん何とか変だもの。}Izumi-san acted strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれは実力と思えないわ。}I can't believe she gave it all she had.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{とにかく、明日もう一度話してみるわ。}At any rate, I'll try talking to them tomorrow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{無駄よ、無駄。}It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{退部直ぐに決まってます。}I'm positive they'll drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。絶対に退部させないわ。}I absolutely won't let them do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{—強情ね。\N—あなたこそ。}– You're so stubborn.\N– Same goes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへ。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいや、XXX。}I'm trying to be a realist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテンにお任せするわ。}I'll leave it to you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみる。}I'll take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしの力で四天王を説得してみせる。}I'll show you that I can persuade the Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、それで三人の退部届は揃ったわけない。}Well then, now that we have our letters ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、泉さんは？}Where's Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはさ、お休みらしいの。}Seems like she's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうせ、退部届らすなら四人に一緒にと思ったのに。}I thought we'd deliver the letters with all four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体どうしたかしら、泉さん。}I wonder what happened to Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{昨日のショックは大きいなのね。}Yesterdays game must've gotten to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{きっと。}Surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{《泉》}《Izumi family》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{いや。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり。}Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{いやったら、いや。}By "no" I mean "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{大の病院なんかいつもんですか、絶対いや。}I don't want to go to the hospital again.{ZZZ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、とても痛そうじゃないの。}But it looks very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{その腕で試合をするなんて無茶ですよ。}Playing more with that arm is reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね。}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、早く。}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{お母さんも一緒に来ますから。ね？}I'll go with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなに行きたきゃ、お母さん一人で行けば良いじゃない。}If you want to go that much, then go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはいやよ。}I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり！}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{お待ちに…！}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり！}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{で、君には説得する自身があるのか？}So, do you think you'll be able to persuade them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。それで実は困ってるの。}Hm. To be honest, I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、何か良い考えないかしら。}Hey, maybe you can think of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{昨日は弾みであんなこと言っちゃったけど、正直などこはあの人達と仲良くする何てできそうにないんもね。}I said that in the heat of the moment yesterday, but I honestly don't think I can make friends with these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{だけど、君達だって、四天王だって…バレーを愛することに軽いはないんだろ。}But both you and the Big Four share the love for the volleyball, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはもちろんよ。}Of course we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{それだったらさ…なぜチームが組めれないんだよ。}Why can't you join forces then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達のどっかに誤解なるとしか考えられないね。}I can't help but think you've misunderstood each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{世の中には虫が付かないってこともあるわ。}In this world there are things that even bugs won't touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへ。}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{大体、君は頭にXXXだからな。}You can be harsh at times, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{それに、早川くんの時だって、殴り合い寸前に成ったそうじゃないか。}I just remembered how you almost got in a fight with Hayakawa-san in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、いやだ、知ってたの？}Ah, you knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{さすが新聞部は早耳ね。}That's a newspaper club member for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あなたたち…}Ah, you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{は。}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{—色々お世話になりました。\N—へ？}– Sorry for all the trouble.\N– Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{—あたしたちはバレー部を辞めるの。\N—ま。}– We're quitting the volleyball club.\N– Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、この通り見てよ。}See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{退部届よ。今本郷先生に持ってく途中。}It's a resignation letter. We're on the way to professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな…}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたち、バレーに命をかけていたじゃないの。それなのに…}You girls, haven't you staked everything on the volleyball so far? And yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{命をかけた？ご冗談でしょう。}"Staked everything"? Don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんなボール遊び何か…}It's just a stupid ball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{嘘！}You're not serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしには分かるわ。}I understand it more than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなた方は嘘を付いてるの。}There's no way you're thinking that seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーバカに成ったあたしだから分かるわ。}I'm a fool for volleyball too, so I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{遊び半分の練習で、あなたたちほどの実力は付く分けないわ。}Training half for fun, unlike you, I can't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうでしょう？}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{フフフ。その実力者を破ったXXXは、天才だとでも言いたいの。}Fufufu. In other words, you're telling us we're geniuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{何ですって？}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、行きましょうよ。}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って！}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{意地を張るのは止して。ね？}Don't be stubborn. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{—よく考えて…\N—XXXたくさんよ。}– Please think it ove—\N– We've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{—行こう、行こう。\N—行こう。}Let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{このままでしておいて良いのか？}Is it okay to let them go like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って！待って！}Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{な、何よ。}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{な…！}Wh—!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{何するのよ！}What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{—ちょっと返してよ！\N—返してよ！待ちな！}Hey, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{返してよ！}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く返してよ！}Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ。鮎原くんは掻っ払いXXXしらなかったな。}Oh, I didn't know Ayuhara-san can handle paperwork well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{《３年c組》}《Class 3C》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{まったく人をバカにしてやりかたね。}What a way to make a person look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{このまま放っとくてはないわ。}We can't let her off the hook like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちやらなきゃ、あたしだけでもやる。}If you don't do something, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。黙ってられもんですか。}Yeah. I won't be staying silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{香取さん。あんたは？}Katori-san. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ…それは、あたしだって。}W-Well, same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{どっか呼び出そう。}Let's notify someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見のXXからなんかどう？}How about the principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわ。}Sounds good. {あたしはそう行ってくる。}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょうどよかったわ。}Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{工藤さん。あなたたちにちょっと話があるんだけど。}Kudou-san. I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{—話？\N—え。}– Talk?\N– Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{授業が終わったら、富士見川のXXX来て。}Come to see me by the riverbank after classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{待ってるわ。きっとよ。}I'll be waiting. It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{臭う、XXX。}Damn it, she left me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{どこにだれが隠れてるか知りやしないわ。}Be prepared for a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX静かね。}It's awfully quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{相手は何人来てるよ？}How many people will be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなこと分かる分けないでしょう。}There's no way we can know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{他の人は良いから、鮎原だけをマークして。}Never mind the others and focus on Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{良いわね。}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{いらっしゃい。}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{遅かったわね。}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんた、一人？}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。なぜ？}Yes. Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、どうしたあたしたちを呼び出したのよ。}Then why have you called us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{聞きたいことがあっただから。}There's something I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{これよ。}It's about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{な、何よ！}Wh-What is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{言ってごらんなさいよ。}Let's hear whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちは本当にバレー部を辞めるつもり？}Do you really want to quit the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。もちろんよ。当たり前じゃないの？}Of course we do. Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはあなたたちと争ってだけど…}I may have fought with you until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもあなたたちの力を尊敬していたわ。}But I have always respected your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたくしだも鮎原さんのサーブとスパイクを尊敬しておりますのよ。}I respect your serve and spike too, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{でしょう？}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのあたしとあなたたちは力を合わせたら、すごいチームに成ると思うけどな。}If me and you join our forces, we might make an excellent team together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{本気でそう思ってるの？}Are you serious about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん。}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、同じバレーをやりからには、試合に勝ちたいわ。}We're in the same club and I want to win matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{少しでも…少しでも強いチームを作りたいでしょう?}Don't you want to make a strong team even a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{同じバレーをやるからには？}We're in the same club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{お生憎様。}Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち…二度とバレーボールを見るXXいやよ。}We don't want to see a volleyball ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、どうしても退部届よ？}So you're dropping out no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{返してよ、退部届。}Hand over the letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたはいくらじゃましたって、あたしたちは辞めるわ。}No matter how much you disturb us, I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーボールなんか糞XXXだわ。}To hell with volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{返してよ。}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{—返して。\N—返して。\N—返して。}Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{—返すのよ。\N—返すのよ。\N—返すのよ。}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{な、何すんのよ。}Wh-What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ…}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなにバレーが憎いなら、こうしてボールを裂いてごらんなさい。}If you hate volleyball that much, let's see you cut up that ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{見にのもういやなボールならずだずだにしてごらんなさいよ。}Let's see you tear that ball you don't want to see ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{それができたら、あたしは諦めて退部届きを返しするわ。}If you can do it, I'll give it up and give you the letters back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが何よ…}Who needs volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが何よ！}Who needs volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなもの…}Such a thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{何よ…こんなもの…}Who needs that thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーが何よ！}Who needs it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールが何よ！}Who needs this ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールが泣くわ。}The ball is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{泣いてるわ。}It's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールは昨日まであなたの親友だったのね。}Until yesterday, that ball was your true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたはその親友をXXXとしている。}Now you're trying to cut that friend to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{煩い！}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{辞めて！}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{危ない！}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン…}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしには…}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしにはできないわ。}I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中学に入る時に誓ったじゃないの？}Didn't we promise after entering Hamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{小沢さんも…小沢さんも。大学へ進んでまで必ずバレーボールを続けるって…}Kudou-san, Ozawa-san… we promised we'll continue with volleyball till high school…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{}Sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{香取さんの言うとおりよ。}It's like Katori-san says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちはバレーを辞めちゃいけないわ。}You can't quit volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXバレーを愛してるのが本当なら…}Since your love for volleyball is true…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜあたしたちはいがみ合ってるの？}Why do we even fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜ手を合おってしないのよ。}Why aren't we united?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{小沢さん。それから、工藤さん、香取さん。}Ozawa-san. Kudou-san, Katori-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{お願いします。}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちと一緒にチームを組んで…}Please make a team with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの親友のために。}For the sake of that friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{あらちょっと。もう一つ。}Whoa. One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら頑張って！}Keep at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{可笑しいな。}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分、どうしたんだろ。}I wonder what chief's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし、XXXにしましょう。}All right, let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんね、四天王を連れってくるつもりなのよ。}Ayuhara-san intends to get the Big Four back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あそうか。}Ah, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{なるほど。}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもさ、今さらあんな連中にペコペコすることないじゃん？}Shouldn't they come to us bowing their heads by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX人たちでもないし、ね。}It won't be this simple. They have their pride, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{遅くに成りました。}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{—あら。\N—まあ！。}– Hey.\N– Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{わあ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{参った。}Here she goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{何が言いたいんだろう。}You've got something to say, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{で？}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{もともと、あたしたちが考えすぎたんです。}From the start we were thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここに来たら、どうせXXXされるんだからって。}When we came here, we thought we'd be marginalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{それなら、先に主導権に握ってやろうって…}To avoid it, we decided to seize the initiative first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう思ったです。}That's what we were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{つまり、あたしたちようかほんの少し神経質だったのね。}In other words, you were a little nervous just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみません。}We apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼なこと言っちゃって…}We've been rude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{へへへへ。}Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{何。分かれば良いんだよ。}Don't sweat it. We're over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{スポーツマン、どうした。XXX行こう。}What's with you, sportsgirl. March with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{—はい。\N—はい。}– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{では、泉はどうした？}What about Izumi though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{—は…\N—あの、それは…}– Ah, she…\N– Well that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日は学校の休んだらしいんだ。}Looks like she's absent from school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちも気にしているんですけど。}We're worried about her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんはこの二三日要すは可笑しかったから…}She's been acting strange since a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{要すが？}Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう言えば、何か隠したりみたいだったわ。}Now that you mention it, it feels like she was hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、あなたたちは大の仲良しなんでしょう。}You're great friends. It must be for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはさ…意外と秘密主義なのよう、彼女。}She's surprisingly secretive though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん…}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理ないわよ。泉さんの母さんて継母だから。}I can't blame her. Izumi-san's mom is actually her stepmother after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{継母…}A stepmother…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{後で行きます。きっと泉さんも分かってくれるわよね。}We'll tell her later. I'm sure she'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{うまく行くかな？彼女(XXX・無意義何と怖さら)ね。}I wonder if it goes well. She can be scary at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉くんはいないと、四天王の意味はなくなるな。}Without Izumi-san, the name of Big Four loses its sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{その通りだわ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生。泉さんの家にあたしは行ってみます。}Professor. I'll go check on her and visit her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、先生。}All right, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、じゃ、あたしたちも一緒に行きましょうか。}Ah. Let us go too then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちは練習、練習。}You should focus on practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし一人で大丈夫よ。}I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。じゃ、鮎原に行ってもらおう。}Very well. Let's leave it to Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{《泉》}《Izumi family》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{大したお屋敷ね。}What a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんください。}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{お留守かしら？}I wonder if they're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{どなた？}Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、あの…泉ゆりさんいらっしゃいます？}Ah. I beg your pardon, is Izumi Yuri-san home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、ゆりのお友達？}Ah, you're Yuri's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.41,0:22:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。鮎原こずえです。}Yes ma'am. My name's Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、そうですか。どうぞ。}Ah, nice to meet you. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆりもう直ぐXXX。どうぞ。}Yuri will be home soon. Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみません。}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも…}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなた、バレー部の方じゃありませんわね？}You're not a member of the volleyball club, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{当たりました。そのバレー部なんです。}Spot on. I am its member.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめんなさい。}I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の方にはいただけないんです。}But I'm afraid I can't let you meet with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{わざわざで来ましたも悪いんですけど、このまま帰っていただきません？}I'm sorry for troubling you with this request only now, but could you please go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、なぜですか？あたし薮から棒にそんなこと言われても、あたし帰るわけにはいきません。}Ah… why's that? I came here out of the blue but I'd rather not go home until I meet with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜですか。}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{黙って帰って。}Shut up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さん。}Ah, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゆり…}Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{帰ってよ。}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここはあんたのXXX所じゃないわ。}You're not welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く。}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{帰ってたら。}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{なぜ…}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{一体なぜなの？}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:55.61,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{こずえは一人泉の家を訪ねたが…}Kozue went alone to Izumi's home, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:24:00.04,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の人間と分かったXX、泉の母の態度はXXXした。}…when it became evident she's with the volleyball club, Izumi's stepmother coldens.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:04.59,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{そこへ帰り合わせた泉ゆりはこずえの腕を掴んで、外へ追い立て。}After Izumi Yuri gets home, she grabs Kozue's arm and drags her out…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:07.95,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{母に大しても激しい言葉をXXX。}…shouting bitter words to her stepmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:12.67,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{こずえは泉親と何か深いわけがあるに違いないと思ったのだが…}Kozue can't shake off the feeling that there's something deeper going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:16.86,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{こんな態度に、こずえは思わずゆりの方に手は飛んだ。}But seeing Yuri's attitude, her hand reacts instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:20.43,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
